text: Monica Lăzăruț (born 13 July 1977) is a Romanian cross-country skier. She competed in four events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Romania Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bistrița-Năsăud County
